This is the README file for Bundle::CPANPLUS.

Please refer to 'perldoc Bundle::CPANPLUS' after 
installation for details.

#####################################################################

* Description

Bundle::CPANPLUS

    Bundle to install CPANPLUS and all it's dependencies
    
#####################################################################

* Installation

Bundle::CPANPLUS follows the standard perl module 
install process

perl Makefile.PL
make
make test
make install

The module uses no C or XS parts, so no c-compiler is required.

